@startuml C-sequence-client-mode-search
title Client-mode search + pagination (useClientList)
autonumber

actor "Admin User" as User
participant "AdminTableToolbar" as Toolbar
participant "useClientList" as List
participant "reactive source[]\n(brand/mfr/tag store)" as Src
participant "computed pipeline\nfilter -> sort -> paginate" as Pipe
participant "DataTable" as DT

== INITIAL LOAD (source owned by store) ==
List -> Src : onMounted -> store.fetch*()
activate Src
Src --> List : loading / error (passthrough refs,\noriginate in the store, NOT the composable)
Src -> Src : source[] populated
deactivate Src
Src --> Pipe : source[] reactive dependency
Pipe --> DT : initial page rendered

== SEARCH PATH (debounced, in-memory) ==
User -> Toolbar : keystroke
Toolbar -> List : setSearch(term)
List -> List : search.value = term
note right of List : debounce 200ms
List -> Pipe : invalidate computed
activate Pipe
Pipe -> Pipe : 1. filter by searchFields\n2. apply filterPredicates\n3. sort\n4. slice for current page
Pipe -> Pipe : pagination = buildPagination()\n(shared util)
Pipe --> DT : re-render (no network call)
deactivate Pipe

== PAGINATION PATH (immediate, in-memory) ==
User -> Toolbar : click page n
Toolbar -> List : setPage(n)
List -> Pipe : page changed -> recompute slice only
Pipe -> Pipe : slice for page n\n(filter/sort already memoized)
Pipe --> DT : re-render (NO network call)

@enduml
